After quite some time Denzabar awakes, a door opens.  Denzabar walks out. 
"System fully operational" A Comp. voice says. He speaks " I am fixed, fully 
fixed" Said he, with joy in his voice. He tried to remember things, he still 
remembered nothing but the past three days. "Well, I still can't remember anything, 
but, This is a whole lot better than grunting." He looked around, looking for 
someone.
